OL,4,CAlabama overturns decades-old ban on
OL,5,Cyoga in schools
OL,6, Yoga can legally be taught in Alabama
OL,7, public schools, after the southern
OL,8, state overturned a nearly 30-year ban.
OL,10,FThe state's department of education had
OL,11,Fbarred yoga in 1993, citing its
OL,12,Fconnection to Hinduism.
OL,14,FThe bill, brought for the third time by
OL,15,Fa Democrat, was approved by the state's
OL,16,FRepublican legislature and governor.
OL,18,FIt limits yoga to stretches and poses,
OL,19,Fand prohibits non-English descriptions
OL,20,Fas well as "any aspect of Eastern
OL,21,Fphilosophy and religious training".
